{"tid":638801,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家用咗幾耐放低","createTime":"2018-04-23T04:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T08:43:44.000Z","uid":8482,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1d12c8a0b92e8b4a785048282524924650038c57","tid":638801,"uid":8482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T04:37:20.000Z","msg":"好辛苦<br />\n而家先第四日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時先可以完完全全放低一個人<br />\n一年零五個幾月呀<br />\n而家先講磨合唔到、性格不合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚掛住佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4e468f9306dc6ed89029d0dfd601e97d0cd1dd","tid":638801,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"我今日第十二日"},{"pid":"eda817a2493f2baf3e43861852527709d85d06f2","tid":638801,"uid":41176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T04:46:39.000Z","msg":"一個月過嚟圍爐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未完全放低<br />\n仲會諗起佢，去到邊度都係同佢一齊嚟過呢度嘅畫面<br />\n仲係唔敢睇電話啲相，都冇勇氣收埋佢哋<br />\n但終於接受咗呢個現實，明白再唔開心都挽救唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開始改變自己希望可能成就一個更好嘅自己<br />\n但不其然會跟住佢之前想我改變嘅方向去行<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e8dc8f271e77cf540b1f6da53717a846c8efad","tid":638801,"uid":175835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T04:54:40.000Z","msg":"放鬆下自己，下一個會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2976fa4b66130b1f5a15e3cb8181bf84ca43f5cd","tid":638801,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:03:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12f783ccd4f5b84d276488e834043fee5718a524","tid":638801,"uid":137976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":